\n<li id=\"cite_note-FT_2015-05-20-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FT_2015-05-20_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Jones, Claire; Fleming, Sam (20 May 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150707225427/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/f48123e2-ff02-11e4-8dd4-00144feabdc0.html\">\"Beno\u00eet C\u0153ur\u00e9 speech highlights central bank links to financiers - FT.com\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Financial_Times\" title=\"Financial Times\">Financial Times</a></i>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/f48123e2-ff02-11e4-8dd4-00144feabdc0.html\">the original</a> on 2015-07-07<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-02-11</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Financial+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Beno%C3%AEt+C%C5%93ur%C3%A9+speech+highlights+central+bank+links+to+financiers+-+FT.com&amp;rft.date=2015-05-20&amp;rft.aulast=Jones&amp;rft.aufirst=Claire&amp;rft.au=Fleming%2C+Sam&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcms%2Fs%2F0%2Ff48123e2-ff02-11e4-8dd4-00144feabdc0.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChatham+House+Rule\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Bloomberg_2015-05-19-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Bloomberg_2015-05-19_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Black, Jeff; Worrachate, Anchalee (19 May 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-05-19/ecb-serves-hedge-fund-diners-qe-treat-most-investors-didn-t-know\">\"Hedge Fund Diners Get ECB's Market-Moving News Hours Early\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Bloomberg_Businessweek\" title=\"Bloomberg Businessweek\">